<SECT2>
 <TITLE>Using probes</TITLE> 




<FORMALPARA><TITLE>Two major uses for probes
</TITLE><PARA>
<UL>
To interface with an object 
To create a GUI to an object
</UL></UL><UL>
<FORMALPARA><TITLE>Interface with an object of two types
</TITLE><PARA>
<UL>
VarProbe: 	   Probes an instance variable
MessageProbe:    Probes a method
</UL></UL><UL>
<FORMALPARA><TITLE>GUI utilities:
</TITLE><PARA>
<UL>
ProbeMap: 	  Collection of Var and MessageProbes</UL></UL></P>
</PARA></FORMALPARA> 




